He gave shelter to Tulasi
that's all,isn't it?

243
00:37:20,504 --> 00:37:22,870
Both Love Music! so only he
did like that!

244
00:37:23,107 --> 00:37:23,505
ls it wrong?

245
00:37:23,975 --> 00:37:27,274
Tomorrow,if any lady customer comes
and talks with me here!

246
00:37:27,478 --> 00:37:29,639
Do you take it as that,l'll leave
you and go away with that lady?

247
00:37:31,482 --> 00:37:34,508
Whatever caste she may belong but
she's as Holy as the Oscimum sanctum

248
00:37:35,019 --> 00:37:38,614
No one gets that Modesty,Obedience
Humbleness and Devotion!

249
00:40:33,264 --> 00:40:37,291
Till now,you are tantalising me
like a hiding gauva behind the leaves!

250
00:40:37,968 --> 00:40:39,128
My desire on you is over!

251
00:40:40,171 --> 00:40:43,197
Now,you go with that music
teacher or go to the hell

252
00:40:44,975 --> 00:40:45,839
ls he God to you?

253
00:40:46,310 --> 00:40:50,406
Mad girl,what can this man be to
you who knows nothing except music?

254
00:40:50,848 --> 00:40:52,543
lf you want go with him
..go with him!

255
00:42:45,563 --> 00:42:45,961
That's all isn't it?

256
00:42:46,530 --> 00:42:47,292
Yes,Madhava!

257
00:42:48,065 --> 00:42:50,431
Somehow Tulasi must get out
of this case!

258
00:42:50,901 --> 00:42:52,095
l'll bear whatever it
may cost me

259
00:42:52,937 --> 00:42:53,801
Understood!

260
00:42:54,505 --> 00:42:59,465
lf there's any crime in this case
everything's of mother,not Tulasi!

261
00:42:59,743 --> 00:43:01,438
Somehow l'll argue and
win this case....

262
00:43:01,745 --> 00:43:02,177
Excuse me!

263
00:43:02,413 --> 00:43:02,777
What?

264
00:43:03,647 --> 00:43:05,114
Butter milk?!

265
00:43:06,150 --> 00:43:06,878
Which one is with lesser salt?!

266
00:43:07,084 --> 00:43:07,550
This one!

267
00:43:08,586 --> 00:43:12,215
Now,my point is that l know the
relationship between you both

268
00:43:12,590 --> 00:43:14,524
But,there's a world at large

269
00:43:14,992 --> 00:43:17,927
Even if a father goes out
with his grown up daughter!

270
00:43:18,596 --> 00:43:20,530
This world talks something
bad about them!

271
00:43:20,898 --> 00:43:23,958
Madhava,l am not afraid of
this world,except God!

272
00:43:24,835 --> 00:43:29,795
The relationship l've with Tulasi
only l & God know about it!

273
00:43:30,441 --> 00:43:31,772
You think about the case!?

274
00:43:43,787 --> 00:43:44,845
You mean to say,you've
accepted this case?

275
00:43:46,423 --> 00:43:47,981
l mean you're going to
argue Tulasi's case!

276
00:43:48,192 --> 00:43:50,092
lsn't it to argue? that l've
taken up this case!

277
00:43:50,394 --> 00:43:51,861
Will you argue and win it also?

278
00:43:52,162 --> 00:43:53,561
lsn't it to win that l
am going to argue?

279
00:43:54,331 --> 00:43:55,593
Then,break that mirror first!

280
00:43:56,033 --> 00:43:56,499
Why?

281
00:43:56,700 --> 00:43:57,632
l want a broken glass piece!

282
00:43:57,835 --> 00:43:59,029
Why? do you want to
stab and kill me?

283
00:43:59,236 --> 00:44:00,703
No,l'll stab and kill myself

284
00:44:01,438 --> 00:44:03,497
You've tottooed conch & discus
on your shoulders!

285
00:44:03,841 --> 00:44:05,706
Are you going to argue for
a prostitute?

286
00:44:06,043 --> 00:44:07,476
Oh! my God!

287
00:44:07,778 --> 00:44:10,372
Whatever you may say,l'll argue
her case that's for definite!

288
00:44:10,581 --> 00:44:12,242
What?...what's the problem
in it?

289
00:44:28,899 --> 00:44:30,423
You're born wrongly to me!

290
00:44:30,901 --> 00:44:33,028
The good advices given me have
become loathsome,isn't it?

291
00:44:33,370 --> 00:44:34,803
Will you bring your own
mother to the streets?

292
00:44:35,572 --> 00:44:37,233
You'll pay for all this!

293
00:44:39,376 --> 00:44:40,365
Sister,you don't feel sad!

294
00:44:40,811 --> 00:44:42,711
Before you come back,l'll
put her into the right track!

295
00:44:43,414 --> 00:44:47,373
l begot a very bad progeny
so only l am going through this

296
00:44:55,259 --> 00:44:56,226
Where are you going off?

297
00:44:56,660 --> 00:44:58,355
l'll deskin you & dry you up
be careful!

298
00:44:58,595 --> 00:44:59,186
Come to the house!

299
00:45:00,764 --> 00:45:02,664
lf we request humbly
you'll not listen!

300
00:45:03,333 --> 00:45:04,493
lf l lash all over your body!

301
00:45:04,702 --> 00:45:06,363
You'll go to any man quietly
as and when l order you!

302
00:45:06,570 --> 00:45:07,229
Come to the house!

303
00:46:59,483 --> 00:47:02,281
Child Sarada,l am going
away from here!

304
00:47:11,261 --> 00:47:15,095
lf we allow anyone into the house
all the sins will besiege you!

305
00:47:15,465 --> 00:47:16,932
They'll go to the hell!

306
00:47:17,234 --> 00:47:20,567
This was a orthodox house so only
l could stay for so many days

307
00:47:20,904 --> 00:47:24,203
Now,with new ideas and if they
allow new people into the house

308
00:47:24,508 --> 00:47:26,874
...l feel like l am in the
middle of a great fire!

309
00:47:28,378 --> 00:47:31,870
Hereafter l can't stay here! l'll
retire in some temple

310
00:47:32,749 --> 00:47:33,716
Are you listening my child?

311
00:47:37,988 --> 00:47:39,580
Till now,lf they had mentioned
the name of this house!

312
00:47:39,990 --> 00:47:42,390
..They used to think it as
pure as the fire!

313
00:47:42,793 --> 00:47:45,057
Now the same people are
abusing this house

314
00:47:45,429 --> 00:47:47,056
Hereafter l can't stay here
my child Sarada!

315
00:47:48,265 --> 00:47:49,960
Father,that cooking aunty!...

316
00:47:50,200 --> 00:47:51,565
My child,go and get my
prayer room ready!

317
00:48:54,498 --> 00:48:55,123
Oh Mother!

318
00:49:03,073 --> 00:49:04,506
Father,the vessel fell!

319
00:49:05,309 --> 00:49:08,369
While,l was coming quickly to
prepare food for the God's offering....

320
00:49:13,917 --> 00:49:16,249
What? don't you know to cook?

321
00:49:22,459 --> 00:49:25,553
When a small girl was trying
to cook with great difficulty

322
00:49:26,096 --> 00:49:27,723
Those who know it can go and
help her,isn't it?

323
00:49:35,472 --> 00:49:39,340
Rituals & traditions are for keeping
a man's heart in right path only

324
00:49:40,243 --> 00:49:43,041
They're not to create barriers
between men by caste,Tulasi!

325
00:59:01,204 --> 00:59:01,670
Next you came in!

326
00:59:08,778 --> 00:59:09,642
Madam,do you need the cart?

327
00:59:21,791 --> 00:59:26,057
Sir,A bad man's sin is taking
a human form in me

328
00:59:26,796 --> 00:59:28,388
l may have expected much more
than my luck!

329
00:59:29,165 --> 00:59:33,761
My wish of serving you remained
an unfulfilled wish!

330
00:59:34,470 --> 00:59:37,962
So,l'll name my forthcoming
child on your name

331
00:59:38,675 --> 00:59:40,074
Have you got any objections sir?

332
00:59:40,944 --> 00:59:43,742
You've only told that Sankarabharanam
means poisonous snake!

333
00:59:44,280 --> 00:59:46,612
The poisonous snake became
a jewel to Lord Shiva!

334
00:59:47,417 --> 00:59:49,578
The poisonous seed growing
inside me!

335
00:59:50,153 --> 00:59:54,954
lf it can reach your lotus feet
that's more than enough for me!

336
00:59:55,825 --> 00:59:56,291
Madam,get in!

337
01:01:45,568 --> 01:01:47,092
Mother,why are you praying
to the foot prints?

338
01:01:47,937 --> 01:01:51,737
Didn't l tell you that,there's one
who's Mother,Father,Teacher & God to us!

339
01:01:51,941 --> 01:01:53,408
These are his foot prints! son!

340
01:01:54,277 --> 01:01:55,574
Oh! ls it of Mr.Sankara Shastri's!

341
01:01:56,946 --> 01:01:57,412
Where's he?

342
01:03:20,263 --> 01:03:21,252
Son,what are you going to
tell him?

343
01:03:21,864 --> 01:03:24,458
Sir,my parents are dead!

344
01:03:25,334 --> 01:03:26,824
Sir,l am an orphan!

345
01:03:28,738 --> 01:03:32,504
lf you feed me l'll serve you
& be at your feet only!

346
01:03:36,412 --> 01:03:38,505
For so many years l had looked
after you so well!

347
01:03:39,448 --> 01:03:41,279
Only to present you
at his feet!

348
01:03:42,785 --> 01:03:44,514
The luck which didn't favour me
if it favours you!

349
01:03:45,288 --> 01:03:47,222
Only to see it happily and die!

350
01:03:48,090 --> 01:03:50,888
Don't worry mother,some how l'll
enter his house!

351
01:03:51,194 --> 01:03:54,129
...l'll learn music from him and
become as great as himself

352
01:07:51,934 --> 01:07:52,764
Greetings madam!

353
01:07:55,304 --> 01:07:57,602
You're a small kid why are
you singing that song?

354
01:07:57,940 --> 01:08:00,465
You're singing of wide oceans do
you know the meaning of it?

355
01:08:00,643 --> 01:08:01,701
....Means....

356
01:08:06,982 --> 01:08:07,846
Oceans means....

357
01:08:08,217 --> 01:08:11,744
When elders in the family've great
difficulties like marriage,ills..etc!

358
01:08:13,689 --> 01:08:15,680
When they're not able to
withstand these difficulties....

359
01:08:16,092 --> 01:08:18,686
They'll say that we are not able to
swim through this family of ocean!

360
01:08:18,928 --> 01:08:19,656
That's the meaning of it!

361
01:08:20,162 --> 01:08:21,186
Oh! ls it the meaning?

362
01:08:21,464 --> 01:08:23,261
Oceans means difficulties!

363
01:08:23,599 --> 01:08:27,228
Look! without knowing the meaning of it
l was singing about myself only

364
01:08:27,403 --> 01:08:29,268
l too have many difficulties

365
01:08:29,738 --> 01:08:32,502
l don't have parents
l am an orphan!

366
01:08:32,708 --> 01:08:34,073
Even that is also an ocean of
difficulty,isn't it?

367
01:08:35,177 --> 01:08:36,735
lf you had a small kid
brother like me!

368
01:08:36,979 --> 01:08:39,470
How nicely you would've dressed
him up and sent him to school

369
01:08:39,682 --> 01:08:42,276
l don't have anyone to send me
to school or good clothes!

370
01:08:42,518 --> 01:08:43,883
Even that is also an ocean of
difficulty,isn't it?

371
01:08:44,153 --> 01:08:48,453
Sometimes,even lf l roam few streets
l don't get even a fistful of rice!

372
01:08:48,858 --> 01:08:51,759
Then,feeling very hungry,l'll drink
water to my stomach

373
01:08:52,027 --> 01:08:52,493
That's all!

374
01:08:52,828 --> 01:08:57,731
For every gulp,l'll imagine it
as some food item and drink it

375
01:09:00,035 --> 01:09:05,029
When it rains or gets very cold
l'll sleep in a corner in some temple!

376
01:09:05,441 --> 01:09:07,671
Like this l've got lot
of oceans of difficulties!

377
01:09:07,943 --> 01:09:11,140
Sometimes,l'll sing this song
sitting in some temple

378
01:09:11,347 --> 01:09:12,507
Then,why did you come
here today?

379
01:09:12,781 --> 01:09:15,750
Only yesterday,l came to know that
this is Sankara Shastri's house!

380
01:09:16,585 --> 01:09:17,347
You're his daughter,isn't it?

381
01:09:18,487 --> 01:09:19,419
...l am new to this place!

382
01:09:19,688 --> 01:09:21,679
Just because you're his daughter
you may not know about it!

383
01:09:22,091 --> 01:09:26,425
Right from useless singers like
me to Great Musicians!

384
01:09:26,829 --> 01:09:29,195
Sankara Shastri is God
to everyone of them!

385
01:09:29,665 --> 01:09:30,689
We don't have any other God!

386
01:09:31,133 --> 01:09:33,567
So only l am sitting at his door
step and singing like this

387
01:09:33,769 --> 01:09:35,361
That God's heart may melt....

388
01:09:35,571 --> 01:09:38,540
And shower mercy on me and
give me a job & shelter!

389
01:09:38,741 --> 01:09:40,675
Expecting this l've been
singing at his door step!

390
01:09:41,777 --> 01:09:44,678
Poor Boy! are you feeling hungry?

391
01:09:45,247 --> 01:09:45,713
Yes!

392
01:09:46,215 --> 01:09:47,876
l didn't eat anything
since yesterday!

393
01:09:48,617 --> 01:09:49,083
ls it so?!

394
01:09:50,386 --> 01:09:50,875
Come,brother!

395
01:09:51,754 --> 01:09:54,052
Thank God! l've got the
priest's Boon

396
01:09:54,290 --> 01:09:55,723
..Now,lt's enough it l get
the God's boon

397
01:09:56,559 --> 01:09:58,390
Can l call you as sister?

398
01:09:58,661 --> 01:09:59,992
You can,what's wrong in it?

399
01:10:00,196 --> 01:10:02,187
Then,sister you don't have to worry
about anything from now!

400
01:10:02,531 --> 01:10:03,657
...Now that your brother
has come to you!

401
01:10:03,933 --> 01:10:04,365
l may look very small
but l can do all the work

402
01:10:08,504 --> 01:10:10,267
Without cutting my fingers
l can cut vegetables!

403
01:10:10,539 --> 01:10:12,006
Without tearing l can
wash clothes!

404
01:10:12,341 --> 01:10:14,673
Then,without spoiling the broom
l can sweep home clean!

405
01:10:15,110 --> 01:10:17,078
Oh God! do you know how many
jobs l can do?

406
01:10:17,279 --> 01:10:17,973
Come and show me!

407
01:10:21,550 --> 01:10:23,347
Will you do the cooking
traditionaly or....

408
01:10:23,552 --> 01:10:25,884
Even that also you want
me to do!

409
01:10:26,155 --> 01:10:28,885
You don't have to do anything
you just sit here!

410
01:10:29,358 --> 01:10:30,757
l'll call you as soon as
l finish my cooking!

411
01:10:55,484 --> 01:10:59,113
Son,lf you touch their door you'll
hear the music of Tanbura

412
01:11:16,305 --> 01:11:20,435
Wherever you place you feet in that
house,you'll hear the basic 7 notes

413
01:11:46,502 --> 01:11:48,663
That house itself is a Temple
for Goddess of Learning!

414
01:12:21,870 --> 01:12:22,859
Greetings sir!

415
01:12:27,943 --> 01:12:28,204
Sarada,why did you allow this
boy into the house?

416
01:12:28,344 --> 01:12:29,538
Father it seems he's
an orphan!

417
01:12:31,447 --> 01:12:34,041
Sir,l am not boy
l am Sankaram

418
01:12:34,650 --> 01:12:35,207
l am an.....
sister,you tell him!

419
01:12:35,484 --> 01:12:36,883
..l can't say anything further
regarding this matter!

420
01:12:39,922 --> 01:12:42,220
lf we feed him,he said he'll stay
with us only doing odd jobs for us!

421
01:12:42,591 --> 01:12:44,718
So feeling pity on him l only
allowed him to stay here!

422
01:12:46,862 --> 01:12:49,228
Sir,even yesterday,l had come
to ask you about this only!

423
01:12:49,631 --> 01:12:50,757
As soon as you opened the door

424
01:12:51,200 --> 01:12:54,226
Aren't there those poltergiests!
hearing their cries & shrieks

425
01:12:54,703 --> 01:12:57,228
Making fun of them,l shook
my hips like this...

426
01:12:57,473 --> 01:12:59,805
You opened the door and
slapped me!

427
01:13:00,109 --> 01:13:04,102
Sir,even if you scold or beat me
l've come to be at your feet only!

428
01:13:09,585 --> 01:13:10,813
My stomach is very small
isn't it,sir?

429
01:13:11,453 --> 01:13:13,853
l'll not eat much...
only this much!

430
01:13:14,223 --> 01:13:15,747
l'll do everything for you sir!

431
01:13:16,125 --> 01:13:17,251
l'll wash your clothes!

432
01:13:17,559 --> 01:13:19,527
Your..and sir,l know the prayer
Hymn also!

433
01:13:19,962 --> 01:13:22,192
While you're doing the prayer
l'll recite it!

434
01:13:22,831 --> 01:13:26,699
Sir,when you take bath,you'll not be
able to reach you back,isn't it?

435
01:13:27,035 --> 01:13:28,161
...l'll clean it for you!

436
01:14:29,331 --> 01:14:30,628
Have you written it? yes sir
l've written it!

437
01:14:30,766 --> 01:14:35,567
Now,the intro will come
here again

438
01:14:36,038 --> 01:14:36,402
That's it!

439
01:14:37,372 --> 01:14:41,809
You have many records and other
things in your home,isn't it?

440
01:14:42,010 --> 01:14:42,499
Yes!

441
01:14:43,145 --> 01:14:44,134
Did you hear this song
at any time?

442
01:14:44,279 --> 01:14:44,904
l've heard it,Master!

443
01:14:45,280 --> 01:14:46,144
Sing it as you've heard it!

444
01:14:56,024 --> 01:14:57,685
Stop it...stop it!

445
01:14:58,460 --> 01:14:59,791
That's the difference between
you and me!

446
01:15:00,762 --> 01:15:04,198
Long back this song was tuned in
this Raga while travelling in a boat!

447
01:15:05,133 --> 01:15:11,834
Now,Buses,Trains,Planes,Rockets
Jackets,Jets everything have come,isn't it?

448
01:15:12,407 --> 01:15:14,102
Speed!...the whole world is
nothing but speed!

449
01:15:14,676 --> 01:15:17,110
How speed has come into our
daily life?

450
01:15:17,646 --> 01:15:19,477
Just like that,it must come
into our Music also!

451
01:15:21,383 --> 01:15:24,375
Regarding this,l've done so
many new experiments!...

452
01:15:25,354 --> 01:15:26,446
...l've found new Ragas
and tuned them!

453
01:15:28,690 --> 01:15:32,490
lf l say truthfully,learning music
from a Maestro like me...

454
01:15:33,729 --> 01:15:34,525
..lt is your luck!

455
01:15:38,267 --> 01:15:40,201
Do you know how to sing
this song really?

456
01:15:40,802 --> 01:15:41,564
How to sing it sir?

457
01:16:25,414 --> 01:16:26,608
Oh! is it you Mr.Sankara Bharanam?!

458
01:16:27,082 --> 01:16:27,571
...Come...come..come

459
01:16:28,116 --> 01:16:30,482
lt's very important that orthodox
people like you

460
01:16:30,886 --> 01:16:34,879
..Should compulsarily hear the
experiments by Maestro's like me!

461
01:16:35,490 --> 01:16:37,515
Breaking up the word into
letters as you wish...

462
01:16:38,093 --> 01:16:40,493
And changing the meaning,is that
what you call as experiment?

463
01:16:41,296 --> 01:16:45,699
Das! A hungry child calls its
mother in a different way

464
01:16:46,568 --> 01:16:50,299
A child got hurt calls it mother
in a different way

465
01:16:51,006 --> 01:16:56,239
A child getting up in the middle of
sleep calls its mother in an another way

466
01:16:56,979 --> 01:17:02,940
Every experience has a definite
Note,Rhythm & Tune!

467
01:17:03,986 --> 01:17:08,616
Das,behind every word of that Hymn
there's heart felt experience!

468
01:17:09,524 --> 01:17:17,124
This song came out of the heart of
a Great Saint in a Trance!

469
01:17:17,532 --> 01:17:18,260
..And this Raga!

470
01:17:18,533 --> 01:17:20,763
With insufficient knowledge and
in the name of experimenting...

471
01:17:21,203 --> 01:17:24,138
Don't desecrete the
Nectar of Music!

472
01:17:24,806 --> 01:17:28,264
The music,on which this Nation
holds it's head high!

473
01:17:29,044 --> 01:17:29,976
..Don't vulgarise it!

474
01:17:31,980 --> 01:17:32,844
Don't know,what's all this fuss?

475
01:17:33,715 --> 01:17:37,082
l don't understand,not only his
song's even his talk also!

476
01:17:37,886 --> 01:17:40,116
Andalu! Did you understand
anything?

477
01:17:40,288 --> 01:17:41,380
Master,l understood it
very well!

478
01:17:41,723 --> 01:17:44,385
Wipe it off! wipe off the
cob webs from your brain!

479
01:17:45,427 --> 01:17:46,519
..Now,learn the song child!

480
01:17:46,728 --> 01:17:48,923
You don't know anything
l'll not learn from you!

481
01:18:00,008 --> 01:18:04,468
Sir,l understood everything you
said to that master!

482
01:18:05,247 --> 01:18:10,549
But,sir l couldn't understand
the meaning of 'Experience' only!

483
01:18:11,353 --> 01:18:13,287
Sir,what do you mean
by'Experence'?

484
01:18:14,089 --> 01:18:15,886
An idea,that a Language
can't fathom

485
01:18:16,758 --> 01:18:18,817
An idea that'll melt
your heart!

486
01:18:19,394 --> 01:18:23,023
Oh! is it? then,isn't there that
'Experience'in that master's song?

487
01:18:23,832 --> 01:18:24,628
There's no 'Experence'in it!

488
01:18:25,500 --> 01:18:27,730
There's Derision in it!
there's Ridicule it!

489
01:18:28,870 --> 01:18:32,704
When we sing that Raga even
stones should melt!

490
01:18:34,476 --> 01:18:35,909
Music in a Boon!

491
01:18:36,778 --> 01:18:42,683
A God given power! Ridiculing
it is a great sin!

492
01:18:43,218 --> 01:18:47,279
Then,shouldn't we sing
like this,isn't it?

493
01:18:47,489 --> 01:18:47,955
You shouldn't!

494
01:18:48,623 --> 01:18:50,989
That isn't the style to sing
that devotional song!

495
01:23:20,528 --> 01:23:21,017
Uncle! come!

496
01:23:21,696 --> 01:23:22,720
lsn't you father at home?

497
01:23:23,231 --> 01:23:25,699
He has gone out uncle,he'll come
back please be seated!

498
01:23:25,900 --> 01:23:28,664
There's no time to sit! do one thing
pack your clothes quickly!

499
01:23:29,070 --> 01:23:29,627
Why uncle?

500
01:23:30,071 --> 01:23:31,663
l and your Aunty are going
to Annavaram!

501
01:23:32,073 --> 01:23:33,040
She's has to fulfill a wish!

502
01:23:33,541 --> 01:23:37,238
lf you also come will us and
have a glimpse of the Lord!

503
01:23:37,579 --> 01:23:40,776
l feel that your marriage time
will arrive at the earliest!

504
01:23:41,149 --> 01:23:42,207
Come on,get ready!
get ready

505
01:23:42,417 --> 01:23:43,281
After asking father's permission!...

506
01:23:43,752 --> 01:23:44,776
Father! what father?!

507
01:23:45,387 --> 01:23:48,754
He never takes you out
no entertainment or fun!

508
01:23:48,957 --> 01:23:51,357
What a father he is?
completely abstruce father!

509
01:23:52,660 --> 01:23:56,528
Uncle,that isn't it!l think it'll be
better if you inform him & take me

510
01:23:56,798 --> 01:23:59,096
Why? Am l afraid of
your father?

511
01:23:59,401 --> 01:24:00,333
Why? will be chop of my head?

512
01:24:00,869 --> 01:24:02,496
You were very young,you may
not remember it!

513
01:24:03,071 --> 01:24:05,164
..Your father used to shiver
even at my thought!

514
01:24:05,607 --> 01:24:07,905
He never used to talk to me
looking straight into my eyes!

515
01:24:08,810 --> 01:24:11,278
He used to go away after talking
looking at threshold,doors,etc..

516
01:24:11,479 --> 01:24:14,073
Fearing that you'll be afraid if
he sees your straight

517
01:24:14,215 --> 01:24:16,740
Shut up,you impertinent boy
l'll tear you apart!

518
01:24:16,951 --> 01:24:17,383
Sir!

519
01:24:21,756 --> 01:24:23,018
l'll turn and pluck out your ears!
Be careful!

520
01:24:23,224 --> 01:24:23,918
...Look,sir has come!

521
01:24:24,292 --> 01:24:27,591
Let him come,today,l'll
wash him clean!

522
01:24:28,229 --> 01:24:31,357
lf l ask him to send Sarada
with us to the pilgrim centre

523
01:24:31,633 --> 01:24:32,930
ls he so brave enough
to refuse me?

524
01:24:33,168 --> 01:24:33,759
Which place?

525
01:24:36,971 --> 01:24:38,871
l and your sister-in-law are
going to Annavaram!

526
01:24:39,340 --> 01:24:41,001
lf you don't send Sarada with
us it's a swear on me!

527
01:24:41,509 --> 01:24:42,305
Sarada pack your bags!

528
01:24:48,516 --> 01:24:51,542
l can't anymore!God l can't
go up this steps!

529
01:24:52,554 --> 01:24:56,456
Hey! Kamudu! l am feeling
breathlessness!

530
01:24:56,891 --> 01:24:59,724
Good! as if the mortar for pounding
grains,complaining to the drum!

531
01:25:00,161 --> 01:25:01,719
..You're complaining to me
about breathlessness!

532
01:25:02,063 --> 01:25:03,121
..Already l am feeling
giddiness

533
01:25:03,832 --> 01:25:05,527
Telling that going to temple
fasting would do good!

534
01:25:05,834 --> 01:25:07,995
You brought me here without
allowing me to have coffee also!

535
01:25:08,503 --> 01:25:09,401
Come on!..move on!

536
01:25:10,338 --> 01:25:13,307
Lord Sathyanarayana!
Hey! You?!

537
01:25:14,275 --> 01:25:17,767
Me? l thought you were
calling the Lord!

538
01:25:17,979 --> 01:25:18,377
Oh! God! it's a sin!

539
01:25:20,515 --> 01:25:20,981
What?

540
01:25:21,416 --> 01:25:24,317
Open that water jug and give me
some water,l'll quench my thirst!

541
01:25:54,983 --> 01:25:57,577
Oh! God! My Golden Glass!

542
01:26:24,078 --> 01:26:24,567
Thanks madam!

543
01:26:31,853 --> 01:26:33,150
Okay! come let's go!

544
01:26:33,721 --> 01:26:36,053
Grandma,we'll sit here for
some time! it's very fine here!

545
01:26:36,491 --> 01:26:38,356
Up there,it'll be better
than this!come!

546
01:26:51,539 --> 01:26:55,703
Hey! l am feeling again
very tired

547
01:26:56,211 --> 01:26:59,510
Feeling it? thank God! please sit here
for sometime and quench your throat

548
01:27:00,915 --> 01:27:04,214
Grandma,for every second step
take rest & have some water

549
01:27:04,619 --> 01:27:05,745
That is my wish!

550
01:27:06,621 --> 01:27:07,087
Here!

551
01:27:49,397 --> 01:27:51,126
Why are you so irresponsible?

552
01:27:51,933 --> 01:27:55,130
That was given by my parents as
a dowry,when l got married!

553
01:27:55,570 --> 01:27:58,801
l was looking after that glass
like my own life!

554
01:27:59,574 --> 01:28:01,201
l don't know,how many dents
it may have got?

555
01:28:21,629 --> 01:28:23,893
Hey! hey! wait
-what happened sir?

556
01:28:24,098 --> 01:28:25,156
What's there in the bag,show me?
there's nothing sir!

557
01:28:25,366 --> 01:28:30,497
Hey! take it out..take it out
l'll give it..give it you

558
01:28:30,705 --> 01:28:31,831
First take it out
here take it sir!

559
01:28:33,941 --> 01:28:35,499
So,small boy,yet....

560
01:28:37,879 --> 01:28:38,345
Grandma!

561
01:28:49,357 --> 01:28:50,346
Have you seen my grandma?

562
01:28:50,925 --> 01:28:52,358
How do l know,who's
your grandmother?

563
01:28:53,628 --> 01:28:55,289
Already she's little crazy,l don't
know where she might have gone?

564
01:28:58,232 --> 01:28:58,857
Grandma!

565
01:28:59,300 --> 01:29:01,530
Stand properly in the queue
turn back sir!

566
01:29:02,236 --> 01:29:03,396
Grandma! Grandma

567
01:29:04,339 --> 01:29:05,636
Please,wait my grandma
is missing!

568
01:29:06,274 --> 01:29:06,740
Grandma!

569
01:29:11,079 --> 01:29:11,875
Hey! Kamudu!

570
01:29:12,280 --> 01:29:13,304
Why did you come without
informing me?

571
01:29:13,548 --> 01:29:15,311
Do you know,l was searching
you all over futily!

572
01:29:15,616 --> 01:29:18,585
Enough of your cleverness! before
that security sees you,join the queue!

573
01:29:18,786 --> 01:29:21,550
lf he sees you he'll throw
you out of the line!

574
01:29:21,823 --> 01:29:22,619
May be this is ladies queue!

575
01:29:22,824 --> 01:29:23,722
No problem! come in!

576
01:29:24,926 --> 01:29:25,483
Did you bring the glass?

577
01:29:25,693 --> 01:29:26,022
Brought it!

578
01:29:43,778 --> 01:29:46,611
Yes move on...move on!

579
01:29:47,048 --> 01:29:49,414
Move on...move on

580
01:29:52,253 --> 01:29:53,185
Come on sir,quickly!..
move on...

581
01:29:54,889 --> 01:29:55,548
Move on..move on!

582
01:29:56,290 --> 01:29:56,779
Sir,you please wait!

583
01:29:58,059 --> 01:29:59,185
Why are you stopping us?

584
01:29:59,394 --> 01:30:00,918
There's no space inside
go after some time!

585
01:30:01,729 --> 01:30:03,390
Look,allow us to go!

586
01:30:03,631 --> 01:30:06,099
lf you want,stop the
people behind us!

587
01:30:06,300 --> 01:30:07,426
That is not possible madam
eveyone is equal here!

588
01:30:07,869 --> 01:30:11,327
Buying a bus ticket for Rs 2 and
coming from a far away place!

589
01:30:11,606 --> 01:30:14,006
When we have come for a glimpse of
God!who are you to stop us?

590
01:30:14,642 --> 01:30:17,543
Look! do you think am l an
ordinary woman?

591
01:30:18,312 --> 01:30:19,711
ln Kakinada isn't there a son
of Gundu family

592
01:30:20,314 --> 01:30:22,282
Do you know,whos'it? he's Head Constable

593
01:30:22,717 --> 01:30:24,412
Don't you know him?
son of Gundu family

594
01:30:24,685 --> 01:30:25,617
...He's my nephew!

595
01:30:25,987 --> 01:30:27,284
Hey! you come in...
come in!

596
01:30:27,555 --> 01:30:28,351
Madam,you wait...wait!

597
01:30:29,157 --> 01:30:32,251
l had a very nice glimpse of God
because of your good deeds!

598
01:30:32,493 --> 01:30:33,551
Even,l too have the some
satisfaction!

599
01:30:33,728 --> 01:30:35,127
My child,how was yours?

600
01:30:35,430 --> 01:30:36,397
Uncle,l too had
nicely!

601
01:30:37,365 --> 01:30:40,300
Okay,you both sit here,l'll
go & get God's offerings!

602
01:30:40,501 --> 01:30:40,796
Alright!

603
01:30:41,002 --> 01:30:42,697
Uncle,why do you take trouble
l'll go and get it!

604
01:30:42,904 --> 01:30:45,099
Will you get it? my child
my great child!

605
01:30:45,306 --> 01:30:48,139
Here take this and get it
get it....

606
01:30:48,342 --> 01:30:49,138
..We'll be sitting here
and get it!

607
01:30:56,851 --> 01:31:01,254
May be we are getting late
for the bus down the hill!

608
01:31:02,423 --> 01:31:05,392
Go quickly and get one packet
of God's offerings!

609
01:31:06,461 --> 01:31:07,155
l can't go!

610
01:31:08,029 --> 01:31:11,487
You must go and get it & then if
you feed me with your hands!

611
01:31:12,200 --> 01:31:13,667
..Till then,l am not in a position
to move an inch also!

612
01:31:16,838 --> 01:31:18,135
Alright,l'll go myself!

613
01:31:18,473 --> 01:31:20,031
Wait! you're old! why do you
take trouble?

614
01:31:20,274 --> 01:31:21,332
Give it to me,l'll go
and get it!

615
01:31:51,072 --> 01:31:51,970
One packet
-4 packets please

616
01:32:25,907 --> 01:32:27,738
Here take this Aunty!
....Uncle

617
01:32:31,245 --> 01:32:32,906
Seems to have given
excess change?!

618
01:32:34,415 --> 01:32:35,746
Uncle,give it to me,l'll
find out and come!

619
01:32:35,950 --> 01:32:37,645
lts God's property! give and
then only come,my child!

620
01:32:38,953 --> 01:32:39,351
Take it!

621
01:32:42,089 --> 01:32:42,748
What's this?

622
01:32:42,957 --> 01:32:43,423
What?

623
01:32:43,858 --> 01:32:46,258
You took Rs 10 but brought
only one packet!

624
01:32:46,460 --> 01:32:48,792
..The balance should be Rs 9.50
but you've brought only Rs 3.00!!

625
01:32:50,965 --> 01:32:51,431
Wait here!

626
01:33:04,211 --> 01:33:05,644
You've given less change,you've
given more change to me!

627
01:33:06,213 --> 01:33:08,374
Settle it between yourselves
why to distub me?

628
01:33:27,301 --> 01:33:30,293
Grandma,take it your Rs 9.50
tie it safely in your saree corner!

629
01:33:30,538 --> 01:33:31,402
Give me some water Please!

630
01:33:31,839 --> 01:33:32,362
Where's the water jug?

631
01:33:33,608 --> 01:33:35,007
You were only carrying
it in your hands!

632
01:33:35,509 --> 01:33:35,975
Yes!

633
01:33:36,143 --> 01:33:39,476
You've missed it some where?
was it any ordinary water jug?

634
01:33:39,680 --> 01:33:40,874
When,l was married....

635
01:33:45,353 --> 01:33:45,910
lt isn't here also!

636
01:33:46,687 --> 01:33:49,212
Excuse me sir! did you see
my water jug?...water jug?!

637
01:33:49,624 --> 01:33:50,716
How do l know,if you ask me?

638
01:33:51,092 --> 01:33:52,218
Go and search,where you
had lost it?

639
01:33:54,362 --> 01:33:55,124
What happened to it?

640
01:38:11,552 --> 01:38:13,543
Look,Sankarabharanam has
come here rolling?

641
01:38:13,821 --> 01:38:15,721
Poor soul,may be interested
in learning pop music!

642
01:38:15,923 --> 01:38:16,912
What do you say,master?

643
01:38:17,291 --> 01:38:21,421
l am saying howling & making noise
at midnight is wrong

644
01:38:22,329 --> 01:38:23,796
Noise and shrieks at midnight?!

645
01:38:26,333 --> 01:38:31,430
Learning for 24 hours a day also you
can't learn even 10% of the pop music!

646
01:38:32,306 --> 01:38:33,739
Have you taken it to be
your 'Prologing Music'?

647
01:38:34,174 --> 01:38:36,108
Learning the 7 Notes by heart

648
01:38:36,443 --> 01:38:38,570
lt isn't like for hours stretching
& pulling one single note!

649
01:38:38,979 --> 01:38:42,847
Your style of Music can be
learnt just like that!

650
01:38:43,250 --> 01:38:44,444
..But our music isn't
like that!

651
01:38:45,819 --> 01:38:47,116
..lt's an ocean..
in that..

652
01:38:49,657 --> 01:38:52,626
Hey! it's useless telling all
this to an illiterate!

653
01:38:53,193 --> 01:38:57,459
Mr.Shastri,please sing your
music go...go please go!

654
01:38:57,932 --> 01:38:59,297
ls it so difficult,that music?

655
01:39:00,267 --> 01:39:01,234
Difficult? its great difficult!

656
01:39:01,769 --> 01:39:04,795
For you to sing 3 words
you've to toil hard for it!

657
01:39:05,639 --> 01:39:07,937
ls it? alright sing
a few lines!

658
01:40:35,529 --> 01:40:37,929
You called our music as
very silly & easy

659
01:40:38,399 --> 01:40:41,300
l'll hum a Raga
please try it!

660
01:41:27,915 --> 01:41:31,146
Music doesn't have differences
of Language & Regions!

661
01:41:31,618 --> 01:41:33,609
lt's an Eternal Flow
of Nectar!

662
01:41:34,655 --> 01:41:38,853
Man from any Caste from
any Religion or any Country!

663
01:41:39,059 --> 01:41:41,220
...Can quench his musical
thirst in that Eternal Flow!

664
01:41:41,762 --> 01:41:48,395
Who are we to decide about
one music as high and other as low!

665
01:41:49,336 --> 01:41:53,432
Without ever trying to learn our
music and traditions!

666
01:41:53,841 --> 01:41:57,038
Your Ridiculing it is
sheer stupidity!

667
01:41:59,279 --> 01:42:01,975
When many foreigners have
accepted the greatness of our music!

668
01:42:02,282 --> 01:42:06,742
..And have been trying to learn
our Traditional Music!

669
01:42:07,454 --> 01:42:11,982
Children fo this country
ridiculing our own music!

670
01:42:12,659 --> 01:42:14,786
..ls like the crime of
abusing one's own mother!

671
01:42:15,529 --> 01:42:17,053
..And a sin like hating
one's own mother!

672
01:42:26,440 --> 01:42:27,236
Pack one kg!

673
01:42:34,381 --> 01:42:35,245
Cost of a biscuit packet sir?

674
01:42:35,516 --> 01:42:36,107
Rs 1 .25 paise!

675
01:42:36,316 --> 01:42:36,839
Give me one!

676
01:42:37,684 --> 01:42:39,743
Subbaiah! l've come to you
for a small obligation!

677
01:42:40,387 --> 01:42:42,014
What? do you need
money again?

678
01:42:42,890 --> 01:42:43,356
Yes!

679
01:42:45,092 --> 01:42:48,858
Sir,how many times can l give
you money on your mortgaged house

680
01:42:50,931 --> 01:42:53,024
Till now,you've given me a lot
l don't deny it!

681
01:42:54,067 --> 01:42:56,365
l am keeping account of
everything!

682
01:42:57,171 --> 01:42:58,968
Some day l'll settle your account
and only then l'll go!

683
01:42:59,673 --> 01:43:01,004
Sir,lts not that,you'll cheat me?

684
01:43:01,508 --> 01:43:02,873
How can you repay it?

685
01:43:03,177 --> 01:43:04,769
All you have is expenses and
not a pie as income!

686
01:43:05,379 --> 01:43:08,439
Alright,lf you don't want to
give it,l'll not force you

687
01:43:09,082 --> 01:43:09,548
l'll go!

688
01:43:09,816 --> 01:43:10,578
Wait sir!

689
01:43:11,385 --> 01:43:14,377
l can understand under what
circumstances,you had asked for it

690
01:43:16,790 --> 01:43:17,882
Keep this Rs 300!

691
01:43:33,507 --> 01:43:34,064
Take it madam

692
01:44:02,536 --> 01:44:03,400
What's this,Gopalam?

693
01:44:07,407 --> 01:44:08,601
...You're missing the beat!

694
01:44:09,343 --> 01:44:12,710
Missing the beat was because of
the mistake l committed sir!

695
01:44:13,547 --> 01:44:14,912
l ditched you & came off!

696
01:44:16,016 --> 01:44:19,144
Sir,for 12 years these hands
never had any work!

697
01:44:20,621 --> 01:44:26,924
Before l die,atleast for once l
must play perscussion to your music!

698
01:44:28,028 --> 01:44:30,019
...l've been praying to all God's
for that oppurtunity sir!

699
01:44:31,298 --> 01:44:33,129
lt's not the question of you
getting an oppurtunity!

700
01:44:33,867 --> 01:44:37,200
People are not fortunate enough
to hear Good music

701
01:44:38,505 --> 01:44:40,473
But,Gopalam this will not
continue forever!

702
01:44:41,208 --> 01:44:44,609
Again,the Traditional music
will get back its glory!

703
01:44:45,412 --> 01:44:47,243
Gopalam,and that day
is not too far!

704
01:44:48,849 --> 01:44:52,478
You've a rock like confidence
so you feel like that

705
01:44:53,353 --> 01:44:58,347
Sir,but after seeing you live
like a king & seeing you now

706
01:44:58,558 --> 01:45:00,287
..My heart is being overwhelmed
by deep sorrow!

707
01:45:01,762 --> 01:45:05,425
Madman! though the property l
had earned vanished away!

708
01:45:06,366 --> 01:45:08,994
..The God given voice
hasn't diminished!

709
01:45:10,203 --> 01:45:13,263
l don't regret on the day l
don't have food!

710
01:45:14,408 --> 01:45:15,841
..l'll regret only the day
l don't sing!

711
01:45:22,215 --> 01:45:25,616
Take this money Gopalam

712
01:45:26,486 --> 01:45:29,080
Sir,are you giving me charity
after taking loan?

713
01:45:30,290 --> 01:45:34,920
Gopalam,we had shared good times
let's share bad times also

714
01:45:35,429 --> 01:45:39,263
Take it...come on
take it!

715
01:46:11,365 --> 01:46:13,890
Though when she was alive
she was hated as a street woman!

716
01:46:14,901 --> 01:46:17,301
l felt really sorry for your
mother before her death!

717
01:46:18,238 --> 01:46:19,899
She died after being
bedridden poor thing!

718
01:46:20,874 --> 01:46:23,069
Once your mother fell ill
your uncle disappeared!

719
01:46:23,844 --> 01:46:28,076
