They came and asked me
l've said 'yes'to them!

957
02:11:38,857 --> 02:11:40,017
Sir's musical performance!?

958
02:11:41,126 --> 02:11:43,856
l thought l'll die without
ever hearing him even for once!

959
02:11:44,496 --> 02:11:47,056
So after many years atlast
my wish is going to be fulfilled!

960
02:11:47,699 --> 02:11:50,224
That depends on his
acceptance

961
02:11:51,470 --> 02:11:53,700
Hey! man! what do you say?

962
02:11:58,644 --> 02:11:59,110
As you wish!

963
02:12:38,517 --> 02:12:48,654
'Sankara Bharanam' Sankara Shastri
Temple of Arts!

964
02:14:05,203 --> 02:14:06,670
Greetings to elders!

965
02:14:08,407 --> 02:14:10,068
l don't have the capacity to talk about
the Art of this Great Exponent!

966
02:14:10,442 --> 02:14:11,909
..Considering it as stage

967
02:14:14,579 --> 02:14:16,740
But,still as his companion..

968
02:14:17,382 --> 02:14:22,581
...l'll tell about the distinction
about this man!

969
02:14:23,021 --> 02:14:28,323
ln past people eagerly awaited
to hear Mr.Shastri's music

970
02:14:28,760 --> 02:14:29,852
..They used get thrilled
by hearing it!

971
02:14:30,662 --> 02:14:34,996
l still remember him living
like an Emperor! Majestically!

972
02:14:35,467 --> 02:14:39,233
l can still visualise that
Pomp and Grandeour

973
02:14:40,005 --> 02:14:44,442
But with time,many changes
had crept into music!

974
02:14:44,843 --> 02:14:47,209
For example,shall l embrace you
shall l cut you?

975
02:14:47,979 --> 02:14:49,970
Shall l bite you or chew you
such Lyrics!

976
02:14:50,715 --> 02:14:53,343
Music that resumbles the shivers
of a Malarial patient

977
02:14:53,885 --> 02:14:54,579
...Have come to the fore!

978
02:14:55,320 --> 02:15:00,280
Many sounds,shrieks!...
cries,shouts..deep sighs!

979
02:15:00,826 --> 02:15:02,088
Have crept into music!

980
02:15:02,961 --> 02:15:06,692
At this juncture,when there was no
support for his music!

981
02:15:07,165 --> 02:15:09,963
..Mr Shastri inside the 4 walls
of his house!

982
02:15:12,471 --> 02:15:15,463
Considering all living creatures as
Music Loving Audience!

983
02:15:16,174 --> 02:15:18,972
Has been practising his
music uninterruptedly!

984
02:15:19,478 --> 02:15:22,538
The traditional music which
is his life!

985
02:15:23,381 --> 02:15:26,248
..Seeing such a stupendous
reception for his music

986
02:15:26,952 --> 02:15:29,978
...A new brightness is seen on the
face this Great Sage!

987
02:15:30,622 --> 02:15:35,924
That Mr.Shastri be blessed with power to
mesmerise us with his music

988
02:15:36,495 --> 02:15:39,623
l pray God to bless him
with that power!

989
02:15:39,698 --> 02:15:40,164
Thank you!

990
02:15:45,203 --> 02:15:46,329
Greetings to everyone

991
02:15:48,707 --> 02:15:54,737
The Lamp of Traditional Music which is
flickering with he storm of western music

992
02:15:55,847 --> 02:16:00,011
l don't know who's that benefactor
trying to protect it!

993
02:16:01,286 --> 02:16:03,584
..l am bowing to him
a million times

994
02:16:07,425 --> 02:16:10,019
The lndian culture which is
getting weakened!

995
02:16:10,462 --> 02:16:11,520
..And traditions...

996
02:16:12,097 --> 02:16:15,089
..The Great Soul who's working for
its resurrection

997
02:16:15,867 --> 02:16:18,165
..l am bowing my head and greeting
him by bowing at his feet

998
02:16:24,276 --> 02:16:25,538
This Art from is a Living Art!

999
02:16:26,845 --> 02:16:27,869
lt has no begining!

1000
02:16:29,147 --> 02:16:30,273
..There's no end to it!

